                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>There is no indication from documentation in Department of State files where and
                    precisely what time this meeting took place. The information set forth above is
                    derived from the telegraphic report printed <hi rend="italic">infra</hi> and a
                    very brief note on the meeting also in file 740.5/2–2152.</p>
